OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Roberto
OL,4,CCavalli dies aged 83
OL,6,Ffashion designer Roberto Cavalli,
OL,7,Fknown for a flamboyant and glamorous
OL,8,Fstyle, has died at age 83, his company
OL,9,Fannounced on Instagram.
OL,11,F"Dear Roberto, you may not be
OL,12,Fphysically here with us anymore but I
OL,13,Fknow I will feel your spirit with me
OL,14,Falways," Fausto Puglisi, creative
OL,15,Fdirector at Roberto Cavalli since
OL,16,FOctober 2020, wrote in the social
OL,17,Fmedia post.
OL,19,F"Your name will continue on, a beacon
OL,20,Fof inspiration for others, and
OL,21,Fespecially for me," Puglisi added.
