OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Roberto
OL,4,CCavalli dies aged 83
OL,6,FCavalli died at his home in his native
OL,7,FFlorence after a long illness that
OL,8,Fsignificantly worsened in recent days,
OL,9,Fthe Italian news agency ANSA reported.
OL,11,FThe Italian-born designer became
OL,12,Frenowned in the early 1970s for his
OL,13,Fanimal prints and for a "sexy style"
OL,14,Fthat remained his trademark throughout
OL,15,Fhis long career.
OL,17,FThe company named after Cavalli shared
OL,18,Fits condolences with his family.
