OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Roberto
OL,4,CCavalli dies aged 83
OL,6,F"His legacy remains a constant source
OL,7,Fof inspiration," said Sergio Azzolari,
OL,8,FCEO at the Roberto Cavalli fashion
OL,9,Fhouse.
OL,11,FBrazilian model Adriana Lima is among
OL,12,Fthose paying tribute to Italian
OL,13,Ffashion designer Roberto Cavalli, who
OL,14,Fhas died aged 83.
OL,16,FThe Victoria's Secret model described
OL,17,FCavalli as a "legend" and shared a
OL,18,Fpicture of her with the fashion
OL,19,Fdesigner on her Instagram stories.
