OL,6,FShe wrote: "Unapologetic in style and
OL,7,Fspirit. We lost a legend today. Rest
OL,8,Fin peace."
OL,10,FThe mayor of Florence Dario Nardella
OL,11,Falso recognised the death writing on
OL,12,FX, formerly Twitter: "We learn with
OL,13,Fdeep sorrow of the passing of the
OL,14,Fgreat Florentine designer Roberto
OL,15,FCavalli.
OL,17,F"He left his mark on the modern
OL,18,Flanguage of Italian fashion. We will
OL,19,Fnot forget his genius and his
OL,20,Funconditional love for Florence. A hug
OL,21,Fto his family and friends"
