OL,3,CItalian fashion designer Roberto
OL,4,CCavalli dies aged 83
OL,6,FFormer Spice Girl and fashion designer
OL,7,FVictoria Beckham has paid tribute to
OL,8,FRoberto Cavalli describing him as an
OL,9,F"icon".
OL,11,FThe Italian fashion designer died at
OL,12,Fthe age of 83, his company announced
OL,13,Fon Instagram on Friday.
OL,15,FSharing a tribute on her Instagram
OL,16,Fstories, Beckham posted a photo of
OL,17,Fherself holding hands with Cavalli
OL,18,Fwhilst he had his hand raised and made
OL,19,Fthe peace sign.
